content: The parents of Lavalette Miller were Joseph Samuels Miller and Marie Therese Gardner. Joseph Samuels Miller was born on August 17, 1848, in Barboursville, Cabell County, Virginia (now West Virginia), and died on February 22, 1921, in Huntington, Wayne County, West Virginia. Marie Therese Gardner was born on October 16, 1858, in Cabell County, Virginia (now West Virginia), and died on January 20, 1932, in Lexington, Davidson County, North Carolina.
